The '''NightMight 4NS''' was a removable [[Scope/Legends|scope]] used with the [[Czerka Arms/Legends|Czerka Corporation]] [[Outland rifle/Legends|Outland rifle]] favored on backwater [[Planet/Legends|worlds]] such as [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] and [[Kalee/Legends|Kalee]]. The scope enabled the user to see heat signatures and possessed a built-in [[Rangefinder/Legends|rangefinder]], enhancing accuracy in low-light conditions. The Outland rifle had a range of 1,500 [[Meter/Legends|meters]] and an optimal range of 700 meters.<ref name="Lord of War">{{Hyperspace|url=hyperspace/member/insideronline/86/indexp2.html|text=The Story of General Grievous: Lord of War|int=The Story of General Grievous: Lord of War}}</ref>

